OL,10,G1555FCastle
OL,11,     GWhen a museum curator's death -
OL,12,     Gcrushed by a falling gargoyle -
OL,13,     Gis linked to the tomb of a Mayan
OL,14,     Gking, Castle worries that he
OL,15,     Gcould be the next victim of an
OL,16,     Gancient curse.
